data.description: Wrap/Seller Financing possiblility. FORMER MODEL HOME. A perfect Lock & Leave or a permenant retreat! Loaded with upgrades! This home offers a BEAUTIFUL designer kitchen featuring white shaker cabinets and white quartz counters, custom tile backsplash, stainless steel appliances, gas stove and oven and tons of storage space. This bright open floor plan includes a spacious main level primary suite with custom-built walk-in closet, 10' ceilings, crown molding and plantation shutters. Second level includes bedroom, full bath and loft with lots of natural light and a loft large enough for a Murpghy bed! Owned R/0 System and water softer, Surround sound, epoxy sealed garage floor and more! Located in gated community of Avier West with a heated community pool.
